text: Ærest on eoccen æt sandfordinga gemære.
Swa ut ongean stream to snitan ige.
And swa on baccan mor middeweardne.
Swa andlang mores on fisclace innan crypeles heale.
<../images/tbar.gif>hit sticað up on þa readan dic.
Of bradan more to preosthamme up on myos wyllan.
Of myos wyllen on þene hricg weg.
Andlang hrycgeweges to þam cristes mæle.
Þonne suð<../images/tbar.gif>hit sticoð eft on Eoccen<../images/tbar.gif>hit onfeng.
